halter about his neckthat neck, which, in her
young thought, her arms were to have encircled
onlynor shall she shut her eyes upon the last
scenenor close her ears to the last groan of my
victim. She shall see and hear all, or comply
with all that I demand. It must be donebut
how? How shall I see herhow obtain her
presence
how
